paragraphs.text:
%spark
import org.apache.spark.sql._
import org.apache.spark.sql.functions._
import org.apache.spark.sql.types._
import spark.implicits._

/* import the goodreads dataset - all data is located at /odsc root folder in the docker container */
final val BaseFilePath = "file:///learn"
val df = spark.read
    .format("csv")
    .option("delimiter",",")
    .option("header", "true")
    .option("inferSchema", "true")
    .load(s"$BaseFilePath/books.csv")
    .toDF("bookID","title","authors","average_rating","isbn","isbn13","language_code","num_pages","ratings_count","text_reviews_count")
